{#
Purpose: Markdown benchmark report template for GitHub, tickets and lightweight sharing.
Input/Output: Receives the final report JSON-like payload and renders a readable Markdown summary.
Important invariants: Keep tables concise enough to render well in GitHub and chat tools.
How to debug: If sections are missing, inspect the report payload keys before changing the template.
#}
# LLM Benchmark Report

## Benchmark Info

- Run ID: `{{ report.benchmark_info.benchmark_run_id }}`
- Benchmark: `{{ report.benchmark_info.benchmark_name }}`
- Suite: `{{ report.benchmark_info.suite }}`
- Started: `{{ report.benchmark_info.run_started_at }}`
- Finished: `{{ report.benchmark_info.run_finished_at }}`
- Records: `{{ report.benchmark_info.measured_records }}` measured, `{{ report.benchmark_info.warmup_records }}` warmup

## Ranking

| Rank | Model | Provider | Avg Total Score | Success Rate | Validation Pass Rate | Avg Duration (ms) |
| --- | --- | --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |
{% for item in report.rankings %}
| {{ item.rank }} | {{ item.model_label }} | {{ item.provider }} | {{ "%.2f"|format(item.avg_total_score) }} | {{ "%.2f"|format(item.success_rate * 100) }}% | {{ "%.2f"|format(item.validation_pass_rate * 100) }}% | {{ "%.2f"|format(item.avg_duration_ms) }} |
{% endfor %}

## Model Summaries

{% for model in report.models %}
### {{ model.model_label }}

- Provider: `{{ model.provider }}`
- Endpoint: `{{ model.base_url }}`
- Model Name: `{{ model.model_name }}`
- Streaming: `{{ model.supports_streaming }}`
- Tools: `{{ model.supports_tools }}`
- Structured Output: `{{ model.supports_structured_output }}`
{% if model.summary %}
- Avg Total Score: `{{ model.summary.avg_total_score }}`
- Success Rate: `{{ (model.summary.success_rate * 100)|round(2) }}%`
- Validation Pass Rate: `{{ (model.summary.validation_pass_rate * 100)|round(2) }}%`
{% endif %}

{% endfor %}
## Strengths

{% for item in report.strengths %}
- {{ item.summary }}
{% endfor %}

## Weaknesses

{% for item in report.weaknesses %}
- {{ item.summary }}
{% endfor %}

## Anomalies

{% if report.anomalies %}
{% for item in report.anomalies %}
- {{ item.summary }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- No major anomalies detected in the measured runs.
{% endif %}

## Recommendations

{% for item in report.recommendations %}
- [{{ item.priority|upper }}] {{ item.summary }}
{% endfor %}

## Fairness Notes

{% for note in report.fairness_notes %}
- {{ note }}
{% endfor %}

## Failed Runs

{% if report.failed_runs %}
| Model | Test Case | Phase | Success | Validation | Error Type | Error Message |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
